Spikes	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.ReefWarriorClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The reef warrior may cause sharp coral spikes to grow out of his flesh. Any armor he wears must be specially designed to accommodate this, increasing the base cose of the armor by 50%%. if the reef warrior makes a successfull grapple attack, the spikes deal 2d6 points of piercing famage. The reef warrior can also form the equivalent of a halfspear at will, so he is always armed.	KEY:Reef Warrior ~ Spikes																										SORTKEY:Class_Reef Warrior	SOURCEPAGE:Ssh
